  <description>
    <p>Tauon Music Box is a music player for playback of audio files.</p>
    <p>Uses a drag and drop to playlist paradigm for easy file importing. Packed with features while maintaining a modern streamlined interface. Allows you to manage your music collection with built-in functions such as file renaming, cover art downloading and file deleting.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Compatible with most common audio files including MP3, FLAC, APE, TTA, M4A and OGG</li>
      <li>Gapless playback by default</li>
      <li>Built in CUE sheet detection</li>
      <li>Groups tracks by folder</li>
      <li>Easily create and manage playlists</li>
      <li>Quick and powerful searching</li>
      <li>Scrobble and love tracks to last.fm</li>
      <li>Large album art and gallery layouts available</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

